bilingual.source: The custom continues to prevail in rural areas.
bilingual.target: 这种习俗在农村地区仍然盛行。

bilingual.source: In that country, traditional customs still prevail.
bilingual.target: 在那个国家，传统习俗仍然盛行。

bilingual.source: Accompanied with the prevail of finance lease, the problem existed in finance lease also arises.
bilingual.target: 伴随着融资租赁业的盛行, 融资租赁业务中所存在的问题也日益凸现.

bilingual.source: In the end, good will prevail over evil.
bilingual.target: 最终，善良将占优势于邪恶。

bilingual.source: Honesty will always prevail in the long run.
bilingual.target: 从长远来看，诚实总会占优势。

bilingual.source: We firmly believe that truth will always prevail.
bilingual.target: 我们坚信真理总会胜利。

bilingual.source: She believes that Pravda will prevail in the end.
bilingual.target: 她相信最终真理会战胜一切。

bilingual.source: Logic and reason should prevail in decision-making.
bilingual.target: 在决策中，逻辑和理性应该占优势。

bilingual.source: Despite the challenges, they believe that justice will prevail.
bilingual.target: 尽管面临挑战，他们相信正义终将占优势。

bilingual.source: She proved through her experience that perseverance will prevail.
bilingual.target: 她用自己的经历证明了铁杵磨成针的道理。

yingyinNormal.en: Gore Vidal once wrote that power is an end to itself, and the instinctive urge to prevail the most important single human trait.
yingyinNormal.zh: 戈尔·维达尔曾写道，权力是其自身的终结，而夺取胜利的本能冲动是人类最为重要的特性。

word_usage.usage: prevail作不及物动词，表示“打败；战胜”时，常与against/over连用，如：prevail against natural selection
prevail的现在分词prevailing，常用作形容词，意为“普遍的；盛行的”，可用于名词之前，修饰该名词，如：the prevailing view 主流观点。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: prove more powerful than opposing forces

examination_example.sentence: For now, though, life <highlight>prevails</highlight>-even in a lake that kills almost everything it touches.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，就目前而言，即使在一个几乎杀死了它所接触到的一切的湖泊中，生命依然存在。

examination_example.sentence: There will probably be months of legal confrontation, and it is not at all clear which side will <highlight>prevail</highlight> in court.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 可能会有几个月的法律对抗，目前还不清楚哪一方会在法庭上胜诉。

examination_example.sentence: If you are at home trying to decide where to go for dinner, however, the knowledge component may <highlight>prevail</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，如果你在家里试图决定去哪里吃饭，那么知识部分可能占上风。

sense_info_list.en: be widespread in a particular area at a particular agent

examination_example.sentence: This is surprising when you consider the <highlight>prevailing</highlight> emphasis by scholars and trainers and managers on the importance of cultivating close interpersonal relationships at work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你考虑到学者、教练和管理者在工作中培养亲密人际关系盛行的重要性时，这是令人惊讶的。

examination_example.sentence: Farmers and consumers alike can choose whether or not to use whichever version <highlight>prevails</highlight>: "I'm giving people an option."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 农民和消费者都可以选择是否使用流行的版本：“我给人们一个选择。”

examination_example.sentence: It was in conformity to the <highlight>prevailing</highlight> practice in the market.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这符合市场上的流行做法。
